quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  26,70,Jabke usne apne baap aur apni qaum se pucha tha ke “yeh kya cheezein hain jinko tum poojhte ho?”
  26,71,Unhon ne jawab diya “ kuch buth (idols/murtiyan) hain jinki hum pooja karte hain aur inhi ki sewa mein hum lagey rehte hain”
  26,72,Usne pucha “kya yeh tumhari sunte hain jab tum inhein pukarte ho
  26,73,Ya yeh tumhein kuch nafaa ya nuqsaan pahunchate hain?”
  26,74,"Unhon ne jawab diya “ nahin , balke humne apne baap dada ko aisa hi karte paya hai”"
  26,75,Ispar Ibrahim ne kaha “ kabhi tumne (aankhein khol kar) un cheezon ko dekha bhi jinki bandagi tum
  26,76,Aur tumhare pichle baap dada baja latey rahey
  26,77,"Mere to yeh sab dushman hain, bajuz ek Rubb ul aalameen ke"
  26,78,"Jisne mujhey paida kiya, phir wahi meri rehnumayi farmata hai"
  26,79,Jo mujhey khilata aur pilata hai
  26,80,Aur jab main bimar ho jaata hoon to wahi mujhey shifa deta hai
  26,81,Jo mujhey maut dega aur phir dobara mujhko zindagi bakshega
  26,82,Aur jissey main umeed rakhta hoon ke roz e jaza mein woh meri khata maaf farmadega”
  26,83,"(iske baad Ibrahim ne dua ki) “Aey mere Rubb, mujhey hukum ata kar aur mujhko salihon (neik logon) ke saath mila"
  26,84,Aur baad ke aane walon mein mujhko sacchi naamwari ata kar
  26,85,Aur mujhey jannat e naeem ke warison (inheritors) mein shamil farma
  26,86,Aur mere baap ko maaf karde ke beshak woh gumraah logon mein se hai
  26,87,Aur mujhey us din ruswa na kar jabke sab log zinda karke uthaye jayenge
  26,88,Jabke na maal koi faiyda dega na Aulad
  26,89,Bajuz iske ke koi shaks qalb-e-saleem (sound heart) liye huey Allah ke huzur haazir ho”
  26,90,(Us roz) jannat parheizgaaron ke qareeb le aayi jayegi
  26,91,Aur dozakh behke huey logon ke saamne khol di jayegi
  26,92,Aur unsey pucha jayega ke “ab kahan hai woh jinki tum khuda ko chodh kar ibadat karte thay
  26,93,Kya woh tumhari kuch madad kar rahey hain ya khud apna bachao kar sakte hain?”
  26,94,Phir woh mabood aur yeh behke huey log
  26,95,Aur Iblis ke lashkar sabke sab ismein upar taley dhakeil diye jayenge
  26,96,Wahan yeh sab aapas mein jhagdenge aur yeh behke huey log (apne maboodon se) kahenge
  26,97,"Ke “khuda ki kasam , hum to sareeh gumraahi mein mubtala thay"
  26,98,Jabke tumko Rubb ul Aalameen ki barabari ka darja de rahey thay
  26,99,Aur woh mujrim log hi thay jinhon ne humko is gumraahi mein dala
  26,100,Ab na hamara koi sifarishi hai
  26,101,Aur na koi jigri dost
  26,102,Kaash humein ek dafa phir palatne ka mauqa mil jaye to hum momin hon”
  26,103,"Yaqeenan is mein ek badi nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar log iman laney waley nahin"
  26,104,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi